com.complexible.common.hash

Class AbstractPrimitiveSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.hash.AbstractPrimitiveSink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrimitiveSink

    public abstract class AbstractPrimitiveSink
extends Object
implements PrimitiveSink

    Abstract implementation of a PrimitiveSink whose methods all throw UnsupportedOperationException. Intended for cases where you want to implement a PrimitiveSink that will only ever accept certain types of values.

    Since:
    2.3
